But it's wrong not to
let you play baseball.

263
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:44,350
No matter who says what,
your father should feel proud.

264
00:16:44,350 --> 00:16:47,390
You can't go to the Koushien on just 
pure luck, without making any effort.

265
00:16:47,390 --> 00:16:48,120
That's true.

266
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:54,650
While studying hard, the players maximized their practice time...

267
00:16:54,650 --> 00:16:57,000
...and somehow managed to reach the Koushien.

268
00:16:58,350 --> 00:17:02,700
Your father, of all people, needs to understand how hard that is.

269
00:17:03,470 --> 00:17:08,630
He understands,
but he still can't accept it.

270
00:17:08,630 --> 00:17:11,130
