professional baseball prep schools...

272
00:17:15,650 --> 00:17:18,650
...that gather baseball recruits from all over the country.

273
00:17:18,650 --> 00:17:20,800
Playing against an opponent like that all of a sudden...

274
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:24,800
Moron ! It's just a matter-of-course 
that the playing field is not level !

275
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:31,650
Climate, environment, facilities, the way 
the players are recruited, the coaches.

276
00:17:31,650 --> 00:17:32,650
They all differ.

277
00:17:32,650 --> 00:17:37,760
But if you keep using that as an excuse, you can't have a national tournament.

278
00:17:40,250 --> 00:17:42,490
Everyone should feel proud.

279
00:17:42,490 --> 00:17:44,270
There's no shame in
 going to the Koushien.

280
00:17:48,060 --> 00:17:49,390
What did he say ?

281
00:17:49,390 --> 00:17:50,170
What ?

282
00:17:50,170 --> 00:17:52,830
You met my father, right ?

283
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:54,650
Your father...?

284
00:17:58,080 --> 00:18:02,040
Aren't you going to ask why
I hate high school baseball ?

285
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:20,560
You swing as though you're going to hit the ball with your hips.

286
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:24,250
Swing from your hips. 
And swing all the way through.

287
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:26,150
